  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our other games</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garden Buddies is a short, cute, casual, and cozy garden sim that lets you unleash your inner gardener. With your companion Mutsy at your side, you’ll create and grow your special garden, engage with multiple fun and easy minigames, and befriend various plant and creature buddies wanting to join you on this relaxing little ride. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/fa10027bb10e787df61e7dc9827ba836.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/35d230ff1e536177c991bbdad9703afe.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/35d230ff1e536177c991bbdad9703afe.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/35d230ff1e536177c991bbdad9703afe.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garden Buddies offers easy-to-learn gameplay with intuitive controls and a clear interface, allowing you to focus on growing your garden without unnecessary complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/6a4434301a14d18efa6a807cae7bd69d.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/7ef29bdfc2189d12fc90f3eec11f8a66.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/7ef29bdfc2189d12fc90f3eec11f8a66.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/7ef29bdfc2189d12fc90f3eec11f8a66.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend a variety of animal and plant buddies who want to join you on your journey. Help them overcome obstacles through fun little mini-games that add variety and fun to your experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/d498088d40c7640f4c03ae7e121e13f8.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ea4c99c3d36c71cff54f08c6fbfc4d27.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ea4c99c3d36c71cff54f08c6fbfc4d27.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ea4c99c3d36c71cff54f08c6fbfc4d27.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond gardening, the game introduces useful basic little life skills like box breathing and grounding techniques, helping you better understand ideas like emotional wellbeing, being mindful, or just the joys of having a smile on your face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/5af38017dd62d1c1014540daf4b0760a.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/1fae091780ce73883e5711f4c8e14a0c.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/1fae091780ce73883e5711f4c8e14a0c.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/1fae091780ce73883e5711f4c8e14a0c.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock decorative items and accessories to personalize your garden. Enjoy different game modes and a soundtrack designed to complement the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ce8601c80f1d9d629ecc2a0d65680a06.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/466648bdef13534687b8da7219de1e4b.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/466648bdef13534687b8da7219de1e4b.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/466648bdef13534687b8da7219de1e4b.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy, 90-minute story mode with engaging interactions and surprises</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple simple minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practical life skills like mindfulness and stress reduction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cast of charming characters and companions to befriend</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization options to make your garden unique</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garden Buddies is a short, cute, casual, and cozy garden sim that lets you unleash your inner gardener. With your companion Mutsy at your side, you’ll create and grow your special garden, engage with multiple fun and easy minigames, and befriend various plant and creature buddies wanting to join you on this relaxing little ride. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/fa10027bb10e787df61e7dc9827ba836.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/35d230ff1e536177c991bbdad9703afe.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/35d230ff1e536177c991bbdad9703afe.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/35d230ff1e536177c991bbdad9703afe.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garden Buddies offers easy-to-learn gameplay with intuitive controls and a clear interface, allowing you to focus on growing your garden without unnecessary complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/6a4434301a14d18efa6a807cae7bd69d.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/7ef29bdfc2189d12fc90f3eec11f8a66.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/7ef29bdfc2189d12fc90f3eec11f8a66.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/7ef29bdfc2189d12fc90f3eec11f8a66.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend a variety of animal and plant buddies who want to join you on your journey. Help them overcome obstacles through fun little mini-games that add variety and fun to your experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/d498088d40c7640f4c03ae7e121e13f8.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ea4c99c3d36c71cff54f08c6fbfc4d27.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ea4c99c3d36c71cff54f08c6fbfc4d27.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ea4c99c3d36c71cff54f08c6fbfc4d27.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond gardening, the game introduces useful basic little life skills like box breathing and grounding techniques, helping you better understand ideas like emotional wellbeing, being mindful, or just the joys of having a smile on your face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/5af38017dd62d1c1014540daf4b0760a.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/1fae091780ce73883e5711f4c8e14a0c.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/1fae091780ce73883e5711f4c8e14a0c.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/1fae091780ce73883e5711f4c8e14a0c.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock decorative items and accessories to personalize your garden. Enjoy different game modes and a soundtrack designed to complement the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/ce8601c80f1d9d629ecc2a0d65680a06.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/466648bdef13534687b8da7219de1e4b.poster.avif?t=1772701181\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/466648bdef13534687b8da7219de1e4b.webm?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429090/extras/466648bdef13534687b8da7219de1e4b.mp4?t=1772701181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy, 90-minute s